{{Flavour|Translocates the caster a short distance towards a targeted enemy.}}

'''Blink Close''' is a monster-only spell which causes the caster [[blink]], always leaving the caster closer to the target than it was initially.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.26]], [[pandemonium lord]]s couldn't cast this spell.

